{"tid":301724,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"老婦哭訴 封路令她一家見不到媳婦最後一面","createTime":"2017-06-29T00:35:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-29T02:08:58.000Z","uid":6604,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d42b34dfa59ad1da6a6d40d416a9e263ac8096ec","tid":301724,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T00:35:20.000Z","msg":"70歲老婦哭訴，媳婦患乳癌住院3年。<br />\n星期日下午6點，醫院急電叫她全家立即看媳婦最後一面。<br />\n但她兒子開車前往，卻用了5個小時，在海隧已經塞了4個小時，夜晚11時才到醫院。<br />\n更離譜的，開車途中汽車竟然被 ___ ___ ___ ___ 攔截並不斷拍打。<br />\n她的兒子去到醫院，受不住打擊，抱著老婆遺體不斷叫「我們回家了」。5歲女兒亦叫「媽媽起身啦」。<br />\n他們之後回家，也要塞很久，到凌晨4點才回家。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ba3376287f45f7c70f0ea8612e14ff752a6443d","tid":301724,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T01:06:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"394b85e7f332aa35b693e027e396109732d2cd8a","tid":301724,"uid":54574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T01:09:53.000Z","msg":"可恥！"},{"pid":"8f8f05a8af4144d8f5671abfe431b03227960562","tid":301724,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T01:10:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2a354e35e94e115a4f148b211190b679bdcde3d","tid":301724,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T01:11:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets